== Thingfish::SQLite3MetaStore

This is a metastore plugin for ThingFish which saves metadata to a SQLite backed
file.

== Configuration

 plugins:
	metastore:
	  name: sqlite3
	  root: /tmp/thingfish/metastore

=== Config Keys ===

[name]::
  Set to 'sqlite3' to use this plugin.
[root]::
  The directory to store the database file in.

